Here's your chance to win 7 Day (6 nights) on @azaleacruise Azalea Yacht Cruise in the Maldives 🌴🌞 

Easy Steps To Win:

1) Click the link in @oceanfanaticsmaldives’s bio to enter!

2) Follow all 26 accounts that @oceanfanaticsmaldives follows.

Tag a friend ( no spam)

Voucher would be valid from the date of announcement till 2023.

⚠️ @azaleacruise WILL BE THE ONLY ONE ACCOUNT TO ANNOUNCE THE WINNER!

The winner will be chosen randomly on August 1st 2021 & announced on @azaleacruise account LIVE.

All included 7 days Maldives yacht trip. The winner selected cannot sell the voucher or give it away. Only the person who won (plus one) can claim the prize.
📷 @jalilnajafov 

Please Note: This sweepstake is in no way sponsored, administered, or associated with Instagram! By entering, entrants confirm they are 18+ years of age, release Instagram of responsibility, and agree to our term of use. (International flights are not included)

node.text:
🌳 Umbrella tree. 😍 How impressive is this holm oak?
Known as the umbrella tree. Once a year two gardeners climb up into its crown on ladders, and for two weeks they prune the tree like a skirt as they meticulously trim it into shape. Its healing powers helped James Bond recuperate – Casino Royale.

📍Villa del Balbianello, Como, Italy.

Credits: @brigrc.

node.text:
Bolivia Salt Flat magic. The salt flats of Salar de Uyuni have proven to be the perfect environment to take pictures that deceive the viewer’s perception of depth!

Credits: @rok_story.
